7.1 Robot Startup Command
This command sequence is used to initialize the quadruped robot locomotion system. The existing Node.js processes are terminated before executing the main robot control program to prevent process conflicts during operation.

</> Bash

cd ~/robodog
sudo node robot.js

7.2 Robot Stop Command
This command is used to terminate the running Node.js robot control process and safely stop the quadruped robot movement and servo activity.

</> Bash

CTRL + C
sudo pkill -9 node


7.3 Face Tracking Turret Execution
This command is used to execute the Python-based face tracking turret module using the Raspberry Pi camera and OpenCV face detection system.

</> Bash

cd ~/Arjuna-Timby/src
python3 Arjuna.py
